Package: ribbitrrr
Title: RIBBiTR R Resources package
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Cob", "Staines", , "cobstainesconsulting@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-1819-3621"))
Description: The goal of RIBBiTR R Resources (or “ribbitrrr”) is to support the empowered use of the Resilience Institute Bridging Biological Training and Research ([RIBBiTR](https://ribbitr.com/)) database. This R package contains functions to facilitate data connection, discovery, querying, and manipulation to meet research and team science project goals.
